A modular Discord bot for player info, gift codes, and reminders for Whiteout Survival.

‚öôÔ∏è Bot Setup & Management
Feature	Description
Automatic Bot Token Handling	Prompts for your Discord bot token on first run and saves it to .env or token.txt.
Logging System	Logs key actions, errors, and warnings in terminal. Shows clear markers when the bot is running.
Command Help (!help)	Polished embed with sections, emojis, examples, spacing, thumbnail, and footer tagline.
2Ô∏è‚É£ User Management
Command	Description
!register <game_id>	Register a user's Game ID. Checks API for validity and logs failures.
!userinfo <game_id>	Fetch player info and display:
‚Ä¢ Nickname
‚Ä¢ Furnace Level
‚Ä¢ Avatar Image
‚Ä¢ State Number (kid)
‚Ä¢ Furnace Image (stove_lv_content)

Auto Update:

Checks regularly for nickname or info changes.

Sends notifications if updates are detected.

3Ô∏è‚É£ Gift Code Scraper & Notifications
Feature	Description
Scrape Active Codes	Scrapes WOS Gift Codes
 for currently active codes.
Notification System	Sends alerts to a configured channel and mentions @everyone when new codes appear.
Commands	!codes ‚Äî Lists currently active codes. Option to configure alert channel.
Scrape Interval	Default: every 15 minutes. Optimized for minimal CPU usage.
4Ô∏è‚É£ Reminder System
Command	Description
!remind <HH:MM UTC> <message>	Recurring reminder (can repeat every 2 days). Mentions @everyone.
!remindonce <HH:MM UTC> <message>	One-time reminder. Checks frequently only in the last 30 seconds.
Time & Date Parsing	Accepts HH:MM UTC (defaults to today) or YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM UTC.
Reminder Updates	Automatic scheduling to avoid CPU overuse and logs reminders being sent.
5Ô∏è‚É£ Future-Proof Features

