Easy to add new features like auto-redeem or alerts.

6Ô∏è‚É£ Other Utilities

Error Handling & Logs: Tracks failed commands, scraping errors, invalid inputs.

Database: Stores registered users and keeps track of scraped codes and alerts.

üöÄ Getting Started
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/wos-discord-bot.git
cd wos-discord-bot
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
python bot.py


On first run, you‚Äôll be prompted for your bot token.

Set the alert channel for gift codes using !setchannel <channel_id>.

